dc_description_s: This point shapefile contains point locations for zip codes in United States from October to December, 2010. Attributes included in the data are polygon (area boundary ID), area/perimeter, county names, FIPS and USPS codes, and alternate names. These data are updated quarterly using the latest feeds from the U.S. Postal Service with additional sources being used to cross-check the data. This layer provides zip code data for view and analysis in GIS and interactive web mapping applications. TTC, Inc. (2011). ZIP Code Points, United States (Q4 2010). TTC, Inc. Available at: http://purl.stanford.edu/zn941hz9515
